        <div class="advisor-role">Executive Coach &middot; Medical Director &middot; Psychiatrist</div>
        <p>Elyse Weinstein is an executive coach, consultant, and advisor with over 30 years of leadership experience in mental health, physician talent strategy, and large-system healthcare operations. She spent her career at Kaiser Permanente, serving as Chief of Mental Health and Medical Director of Physician Recruitment for one of the nation&rsquo;s largest multi-specialty medical organizations. Today, Elyse works with physicians and healthcare leaders navigating pivotal career decisions and organizational change, bringing a psychiatrist&rsquo;s insight into human behavior together with a strategist&rsquo;s understanding of institutional dynamics. She is also active as a venture investor, supporting innovation in healthcare and beyond.</p>
